---
---
<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="scan-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <p class="sec-label">01 — About</p>

  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <h2>From first line of code<br>to <span class="yellow">final pixel</span></h2>
      <p>I write code that works and design interfaces that hold attention. My stack spans
         HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, and Python — plus Android development in Java and
         Kotlin when the project calls for it.</p>
      <p>Wrapping up my BSc. IT at ISMT College in Kathmandu, where coursework in
         databases, system analysis, and cybersecurity shaped how I think about
         building things that actually hold up.</p>

      <div class="counters">
        <div class="counter-item">
          <strong data-target="3">3+</strong>
          <span>Years coding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="counter-item">
          <strong data-target="20">20+</strong>
          <span>Projects built</span>
        </div>
        <div class="counter-item">
          <strong data-target="6">6+</strong>
          <span>Technologies</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="#contact" class="btn-solid">Get In Touch &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cards reveal-group">
      <div class="acard glass-card border-beam-wrap">
        <div class="beam" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <i class="bx bx-code-alt"></i>
        <h4>Clean Code</h4>
        <p>Every project ships with code a teammate could read on day one — structured, documented, and built to last beyond the deadline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acard glass-card border-beam-wrap">
        <div class="beam" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <i class="bx bx-palette"></i>
        <h4>Creative Design</h4>
        <p>Good design isn't decoration. It's the difference between a site visitors trust and one they bounce from in three seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acard glass-card border-beam-wrap">
        <div class="beam" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <i class="bx bx-mobile-alt"></i>
        <h4>Responsive</h4>
        <p>Built to work on every screen from the start — not patched for mobile after the fact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acard glass-card border-beam-wrap">
        <div class="beam" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <i class="bx bx-rocket"></i>
        <h4>Performance</h4>
        <p>Speed is a feature. Every project is optimised so the first load feels instant and every interaction stays snappy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about {
  background: var(--bg2);
  padding-top: 9rem; padding-bottom: 9rem;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}

/* Diagonal grid texture */
.about::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(232,255,72,.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,255,72,.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.about-wrap {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 6rem; align-items: start;
  position: relative;
}

.about-text h2 {
  font-family: var(--fhead);
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 3.5vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.about-text p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.55rem; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; }

.counters { display: flex; gap: 3.5rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
.counter-item strong {
  display: block; font-family: var(--fhead);
  font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--yellow); line-height: 1;
}
.counter-item span { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--muted); }

/* Glass cards grid */
.about-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.6rem; }

.acard {
  padding: 2.2rem 2rem;
  transition: border-color .3s, transform .3s, box-shadow .3s;
}
.acard:hover {
  border-color: rgba(232,255,72,.3);
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(232,255,72,.07);
}
.acard i    { font-size: 2.6rem; color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: block; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(232,255,72,.3)); }
.acard h4   { font-family: var(--fhead); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: .7rem; }
.acard p    { font-size: 1.35rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

@media (max-width: 1100px) {
  .about-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}
@media (max-width: 500px) {
  .about-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .counters { gap: 2rem; }
}
</style>
